title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Russo/Parise/LaPanta
description: #92Noon brings #WhiteHorseRadio to the Xcel Energy Center penalty box for Vox In The Box! Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau stops by to talk about his team's post-Koivu future, The Athletic's Michael Russo previews the matchup against the Oilers, Wild Forward Zach Parise skates over to the box to talk with PA, and Wild VOX Anthony LaPanta talks about the current status of the Wild!
